<C>__{starks}
<D>__{it worked, didn't it?}
<A>__{lorenson nods.}
<C>__{starks}
<D>__{this is really happening, isn't it?}
<C>__{dr. lorenson}
<D>__{[beat] what do you need me to do?}
<C>__{starks}
<D>__{[beat] thank you.}
<A>__{starks folds the letter.}
<C>__{starks}
<D>__{i need to get this letter to someone.}
<C>__{dr. lorenson}
<D>__{i can't take you out of here in your condition...}
<C>__{starks}
<D>__{and i can't stay here in my condition. i am going to die tonight. it's already been decided.}
